Ranger Help for: longshot
=========================

SYNTAX:      longshot <target> or lshot <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   8
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  bow

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to fire a long-range bow shot at a target
in an adjacent room. The Ranger draws the bow with great force and
sends an arrow flying over a considerable distance. This is especially
useful for initiating combat from safety or harassing fleeing enemies.
The damage and accuracy of the shot depend on the Ranger's strength,
dexterity, and proficiency with the skill.
